  "title": "ISic001446. I.Sicily inscription 001446",
  "body": "<div id=\"editions\"><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  <div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  <a id=\"al1-interpretive\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>hο <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Μιλίχιος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μιλίχιος\">Μιλίχιος</span></span> τᾶ-<br id=\"al2-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ς πατριᾶς τᾶν <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"hερ\n                    μίο\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"hερ\n                    μίο\">h&lt;ε&gt;ρ-<br id=\"al3-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>μίο</span></span>̄ παίδο̄ν καὶ <br id=\"al4-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">4</span>τᾶν <span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐκλέα\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐκλέα\">Εὐκλέα</span></span> παί-<br id=\"al5-interpretive\"><span class=\"linenumber\">5</span>δ&lt;ο̄&gt;ν </span></div>  <p class=\"miniapp\"></p></div><div class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Valentina Mignosa</div><div id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\"><div class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\"><span class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\"><a id=\"al1-diplomatic\"><!--0--></a><span class=\"linenumber\">1</span>HΟ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"divine\" data-text=\"Μιλίχιος\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Μιλίχιος\">ΜΙΛΙΧΙΟΣ</span></span>ΤΑ<br id=\"al2-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">2</span>ΣΠΑΤΡΙΑΣΤΑΝ<span data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"hερ\n                    μίο\"><span data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"hερ\n                    μίο\">HΡ<br id=\"al3-diplomatic\"><span class=\"linenumber\">3</span>ΜΙΟ</span></span>̄ΠΑΙΔΟ̄ΝΚΑΙ<br id=\"al4-